name: iShares Core S&P Total U.S. Stock Market Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The fund's current principal investment strategy is to invest in one or more iShares ETFs and/or Index Securities. In addition to or as an alternative to these strategies, XTOT may also invest by employing a Replicating Strategy, a Sampling Strategy and/or through the use of derivatives. The fund seeks to provide longterm capital growth.
